<body>
    <div id="Background">
        <div id="TitleBlock">
            <h1>PennCourseSearch</h1>
            <h2>A better way to find courses and make schedules</h2>    
        </div>
        <div id="ButtonBlock">
            <a href="/register"><button class="linkButton">Sign Up</button></a>
            <a href="/login"><button class="linkButton">Log in</button></a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <section id="Reasons">
        <h3>Why should you use PennCourseSearch?</h3>
        <div class="reasonBlock">
            <span><i class="fa fa-rocket"></i>It's ultra-fast.</span>
            <p>Fewer clicks and quicker load times let you focus on what's important: your schedule.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reasonBlock">
            <span><i class="fa fa-search"></i>It's super easy.</span>
            <p>One page is all you need. Search for courses and view your schedules at the same time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reasonBlock">
            <span><i class="fa fa-ban"></i>PennInTouch sucks.</span>
            <p>But you knew that already.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="Features">
        <h3>Features</h3>
        <div class="featureBlock">
            <img src="/css/welcome/One.png">
            <span>Clean and quick course information</span>
            <p>Search across departments by course ID, keyword, or instructor. Easily compare classes side by side and find the best section and meeting time in a flash. Plus, you can access Penn Course Review ratings to make the best decision about which class to choose.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="featureBlock">
            <img src="/css/welcome/Two.png">
            <span>Smarter and more beautiful schedules</span>
            <p>Adding a class takes a single click. See your schedule update immediately and watch it resize with your browser. Class blocks also show you room numbers, so you can see if you'll end up going from DRL to Huntsman and back.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="featureBlock">
            <img src="/css/welcome/Three.png">
            <span>Consistent updates and support</span>
            <p>Leave Penn InTouch in the 20th Century. PCS is in active development, so any bugs will be squashed promptly. If you have an idea for a new feature, let us know! We're always looking to improve PCS to make your experience simpler and easier.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div id="BottomLinks">
        <h2>So what are you waiting for?</h2>
        <a href="/register"><button class="linkButton">Sign Up</button></a>
        <a href="/login"><button class="linkButton">Log in</button></a>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <div>
            <a href="http://BenBernstein.me"><div id="LogoWhite"></div></a>
            <span>Made by <a href="http://BenBernstein.me" style="color:white;text-decoration:none">Ben Bernstein</a></span>
        </div>
    </footer>
